videos.headline: Adams goes through defender for Cuse TD
videos.description: Abdul Adams runs through the hole and a Liberty defender for Syracuse's first touchdown of the season.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Adams goes through defender for Cuse TD) 2019/08/31

videos.headline: Neal takes off for 42-yard Cuse TD
videos.description: Moe Neal flies through the hole and outruns the whole Liberty defense for a 42-yard touchdown to extend Syracuse's lead.
